# ---- Booking form delivery (Web3Forms) ----
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and enter contact@leanhippo.io as the
#    destination email. They email you a free Access Key (no account needed).
# 2. Verify the email so submissions are delivered.
# 3. Copy the key below, then rename this file to ".env.local" (or set the
#    variable in your build environment) and rebuild: `npm run build`.
#
# Until a real key is set, the booking form falls back to a mailto: to
# contact@leanhippo.io so no request is ever lost.

NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=REPLACE_WITH_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY
